\">Add above ingredients to 50 mL tube. <\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Add UltraPure water to ~40 mL<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Add NaOH to pH ~7 (slowly)<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Add UltraPure water to 45 mL<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Filter sterilize with 0.22 \u03bcm filter<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Autoclave with lid loosened. Recover from autoclave soon after the cycle is complete.<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Pour autoclaved solution into fresh 50 mL tube.<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Aliquot into 1.5 mL tubes.<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">UV sterilize for 10-30 minutes.<\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":[],"data":null,"html":null,"section":null,"section_color":"#A492FF","section_duration":0,"critical":null,"critical_id":null,"duration":0},{"id":1258895,"guid":"714576B678E24F82819AAA1C4FC555D2","previous_id":1258894,"previous_guid":"57DD50CF6ED84FD39DEDEB103CAD2BFC","modified_on":0,"protocol_id":0,"components":[{"id":1054723,"guid":"2B796783BBFC486B9EFB64A5C17E4A01","order_id":1,"type_id":6,"title":"Section","source":{"title":"Hot Lysis"}},{"id":1054724,"guid":"D5093CABCCC343689856E76A87BA0D15","order_id":1,"type_id":1,"title":"description","source":{"description":"<div class = \"text-blocks\"><div class = \"text-block\">Add 1.4 mL of NEB to each Sterivex with syringe and needle. Position the needle just below the mouth of the Sterivex so that it does not come back out the top. Do not fill to the top \u2013 stop when the solution covers the filter. <\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":[],"data":null,"html":null,"section":null,"section_color":"#94EBFF","section_duration":0,"critical":null,"critical_id":null,"duration":0},{"id":1258896,"guid":"EF46188060024D43BE0C60AABD989B84","previous_id":1258895,"previous_guid":"714576B678E24F82819AAA1C4FC555D2","modified_on":0,"protocol_id":0,"components":[{"id":1054723,"guid":"AB9ADEBC8EB04D279DF9CEEB60E1BE64","order_id":1,"type_id":6,"title":"Section","source":{"title":"Hot Lysis"}},{"id":10